title: Queen Elizabeth II (1926-2022) | Daily Best of September 9 | Rick & Bubba
description:
We look back at the 70-year reign of Queen Elizabeth II. Our live studio audience makes it's highly anticipated return to the Golden Ticket Seats, including special appearance from Garry "The Bulldozer Man." Major League Baseball makes some major league rule changes. Fauci says that we "don't have time" to do clinical trials on the latest COVID booster. And, Adler attends a Bill Gaither gospel concert with his grandma.
